


1. Esc - enter to normal mode
2. 0 - move to the beginning of the line
3. $ - move end of the line
4. i - insert before the cursor
5. u - undo the last changes
6. w - save the file
7. q - quit 
8. wq - save and quit
9. q! - quit without save(forcefull exit)
10. dd - delete the current line
11. p - paste the deleted text or copied text after the cursor
12. ctrl+r - redo the last undone change
13. h - move left
14. j - move down
15. k - move up
16. l - move right 
17. set nu - show line numbers
18. set nonu - hide line numberrs
